      <title>随着费用大幅下滑，中国铜冶炼厂将讨论减产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-s-copper-smelters-to-discuss-production-cut-as-fees-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最大的铜冶炼厂将于下周在北京召开会议，讨论应对矿石加工费跌至多年来最低水平的措施，包括可能的减产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-s-copper-smelters-to-discuss-production-cut-as-fees-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 04:21:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚大亨呼吁改革电力行业以重振增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/nigeria-s-tony-elumelu-calls-for-revamp-of-power-sector-to-revive-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚大亨托尼·埃鲁梅卢 (Tony Elumelu) 的公司控制着该国 15% 的发电市场，他敦促政府改革电力行业，他表示这对于重振陷入困境的经济至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/nigeria-s-tony-elumelu-calls-for-revamp-of-power-sector-to-revive-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利：中国需要更大规模的以消费为中心的刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-07/china-needs-bigger-consumption-centric-stimulus-xing-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利首席中国经济学家邢罗宾讨论了政府支持世界第二大经济体的努力。中国高级经济官员周三在北京举行的全国人民代表大会期间举行的新闻发布会上，为中国今年经济增长约 5% 的计划进行了辩护，并暗示可能会增加流动性。邢在“彭博：中国秀”上发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-07/china-needs-bigger-consumption-centric-stimulus-xing-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:55:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>易纲提出计划帮助中国房地产开发商获得1390亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/yi-gang-proposes-plan-to-help-china-real-estate-developers-access-139-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国前央行行长易纲建议中国房地产开发商使用预售资金的新方式，这可能有助于中国陷入困境的房地产市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/yi-gang-proposes-plan-to-help-china-real-estate-developers-access-139-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:42:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
